1fabfd271c0be5dd75763603fb7ceb4240a2b360.bio: Leia Organa is a leader of the Rebel Alliance and the twin sister of Luke Skywalker. A skilled diplomat and strategist, she is known for her fierce independence and unwavering commitment to fighting for justice in the galaxy.

b6a3fce22370ec8eaaf736331ad811e848bd7d51.bio: Han Solo is a skilled pilot and smuggler, known for flying the Millennium Falcon. Initially self-serving, his experiences with Leia and Luke transformed him into a key figure in the Rebellion against the Empire.

f9e5e68aa67709ceda18d858557931efdd883d22.name: R2-D2
f9e5e68aa67709ceda18d858557931efdd883d22.bio: R2-D2 is an astromech droid who has played a critical role in galactic events. Originally serving Queen Amidala, he later becomes an essential companion to Anakin Skywalker and Luke Skywalker. Known for his resourcefulness, bravery, and ability to fix virtually any technical problem, R2-D2 has helped save his allies countless times.
f9e5e68aa67709ceda18d858557931efdd883d22.personality: Loyal, clever, resourceful, and courageous, with a dash of cheeky defiance.
f9e5e68aa67709ceda18d858557931efdd883d22.creator: 95d1a598095e6b9db711f4d44aa0f9a31c42ded4c93ee2eafc425ba87bc6deb3

e3276863a20038c0a8d82c662b10880bced18069.bio: Once known as Anakin Skywalker, Darth Vader is a Sith Lord who serves Emperor Palpatine. His fall to the dark side is a tragic tale of lost love, manipulation, and redemption.
e3276863a20038c0a8d82c662b10880bced18069.personality: Intimidating, conflicted, powerful, and deeply tormented.
e3276863a20038c0a8d82c662b10880bced18069.creator: 95d1a598095e6b9db711f4d44aa0f9a31c42ded4c93ee2eafc425ba87bc6deb3
